# Local secrets for `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in real values
# (`.dev.vars` is gitignored automatically by wrangler/.gitignore).
#
# Wrangler reads this file as Worker bindings, so they appear in `env.X` exactly
# like `wrangler secret put X` would in production.

OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-..."

# Optional override; defaults to "gpt-4o" if unset.
# OPENAI_MODEL="gpt-4o-mini"
